title: Turtle Cake
directions: Mix cake mixture per instructions on the box. Add half to 9 X 13 baking pan. And bake for 15 minutes.
While the cake is baking, in a double boiler, melt 1 Lbs camels and margarine. Once melted slowly add the can of milk.
Pour caramel mixture over cake in the pan and then pour the rest of the cake mixture over the top and sprinkle with 6 oz of chocolate chips and 1 cup of nuts.
